        </div>
        <div class="hub-card">
            <img src="./images/shanghai.jpg" alt="Shanghai hub">
            <h2 class="text-center fw-bold">Shanghai</h2>
            <p class="text-center" >Introducing Shanghai's Leading Distribution Center: Your key to streamlined logistics and unparalleled product accessibility in Asia's economic powerhouse. Our cutting-edge facility guarantees swift, dependable deliveries spanning a wide array of product categories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hub-card">
            <img src="./images/paris.jpg" alt="Paris hub">
            <h2 class="text-center fw-bold">Paris</h2>
            <p class="text-center">Presenting Paris's Premier Distribution Center: Your ultimate destination for efficient logistics and unparalleled product reach in the heart of Europe. Our cutting-edge facility ensures prompt, reliable deliveries across a diverse range of products.</p>
        </div>
    </section>


</div>